Package org.sbml.jsbml.math.parser

Class FormulaParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sbml.jsbml.math.parser.FormulaParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FormulaParserConstants, IFormulaParser

    public class FormulaParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements IFormulaParser, FormulaParserConstants
    Class used to parse infix mathematical formula and returns a representation of it as an Abstract Syntax Tree (AST).

    Support almost the same syntax as defined in the LibSBML C-inspired infix notation taken from SBML Level 1 parser.

    Since:
    0.8
    Author:
    Alexander Dörr, Nicolas Rodriguez
